    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "You mentioned \"fragmented political environment\" and the need to \"integrate\" them into \"core values.\" Some critics argue that these demographic changes aren't just about political shifts, but represent a fundamental erosion of the cultural identity that underpins Western democracy. Do you think there's an inherent tension between the values of these growing immigrant groups and the stability of the existing Western framework?",
